snippet.title: [ Faceless ] PV
snippet.description:
[Faceless project]
"The past is important, isn't it?
If the face in the past is fake, 
Then where is my real face? 
Has it ever existed?"
-----------------------
Art by MadBoris, Lilith Nguyen (Moon)
Music: You're not a devil, trust me by Kato Etsuo.
